Text: Re The WP Discovery Web page is experiencing problems Cc this email are NRUs data responses to DSNI DSNI and DSNI Original Message From Westenberg Sarah A LP To inergyLLCcom inergyLLCcom Cc Burger Peter J LP Wright Jon D LP Casad Kurt R LP Foulkes Gabrielle PGF Date Monday March PM Subject The WP Discovery Web page is experiencing problems Due to server problems that began late on Friday March the discovery web page may not have sent requestsresponses to all rate case parties Technicians are working to correct the problem but in the meantime parties need to send requestsresponses via attachments to email The discovery web page sends to a slightly different address list so I have provided that below If you have any questions please feel free to contact me by either email or by phone My direct number is Sarah inergyLLCcom DSNIRESPONSEdoc DSNIRESPONSEdoc DSNIRESPONSEdoc
